    <h3 id="kadane-and-39-s-algorithm">
      <a href="#kadane-and-39-s-algorithm">Kadane&#39;s Algorithm (카데인 알고리즘)</a>
    </h3>
    <blockquote>
      <p>
        DP의 대표적인 예시 문제로 <code class="inline-code-block">최대 부분합 배열 문제</code>
        가 있음
      </p>
    </blockquote>
    <p>
      <ImgZoom
        src="https://github.com/kingseungil/devlog/assets/109774037/68225d4f-5a8b-4dd8-a34f-e10ff8c9b94e"
        alt="카데인 알고리즘"></ImgZoom>
      <a
        href="https://medium.com/@vdongbin/kadanes-algorithm-%EC%B9%B4%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B8-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98-acbc8c279f29"
        rel="external">
        사진출처
      </a>
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <code class="inline-code-block">최대 부분합 배열 문제</code>
        란?
        <ul>
          <li>배열에서 연속된 부분 배열의 합이 최대가 되는 값을 찾는 문제</li>
          <li>
            예시 : <code class="inline-code-block">[-2, 1, -3, 4, -1, 2, 1, -5, 4]</code>
            에서 최대 부분합 배열은
            <code class="inline-code-block">[4, -1, 2, 1]</code>
            이며, 합은
            <code class="inline-code-block">6</code>
             이다.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <details>
      <summary><span style="color: #b96a38">Kadane's algorithm 코드</span></summary>
      <div markdown="1">
        <div class="code-block titled">
          <h2 class="code-title">code.java</h2>
          <CodeCopy>
            <pre><code
                class="language-java">{@html String.raw`<div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token comment">/// showLineNumber </span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">KadaneAlgorithm</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">String</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> fruits <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">solution</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>fruits<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">// 6</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">solution</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> fruits<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">int</span> currentMax <span class="token operator">=</span> fruits<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">int</span> globalMax <span class="token operator">=</span> fruits<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> i <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> i <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> fruits<span class="token punctuation">.</span>length<span class="token punctuation">;</span> i<span class="token operator">++</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">            currentMax <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token class-name">Math</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">max</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>fruits<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> currentMax <span class="token operator">+</span> fruits<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>currentMax <span class="token operator">></span> globalMax<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">                globalMax <span class="token operator">=</span> currentMax<span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">            <span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">        <span class="token keyword">return</span> globalMax<span class="token punctuation">;</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content">    <span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div><div class="code-line"><div class="code-linenotation"><span class="no-line-number"></span><span class="no-line-diff"></span></div><div class="code-content"><span class="token punctuation">}</span></div></div>`}</code></pre>
          </CodeCopy>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <code class="inline-code-block">currentMax</code>
             : 현재까지의 최대 부분합
          </li>
          <li>
            <code class="inline-code-block">globalMax</code>
             : 전체의 최대 부분합
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <h3 id="dynamic-programming"><a href="#dynamic-programming">Dynamic Programming과 다른 알고리즘들의 차이</a></h3>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <strong>분할 정복</strong>
        과의 차이
        <ul>
          <li>분할 정복은 부분 문제가 서로 중복되지 않음</li>
          <li>동적 계획법은 부분 문제가 서로 중복되어 재활용에 적합함</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>그리디 알고리즘</strong>
        과의 차이
        <ul>
          <li>그리디 알고리즘은 순간의 최선을 구하는 방식 (근사치)</li>
          <li>동적 계획법은 모든 경우의 수를 다 계산해서 최선의 답을 구함</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </article>
